tings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-61634345\" data-id=\"61634345\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6136e29b elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"6136e29b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Moving is one of life\u2019s biggest transitions. I\u2019ve done it across countries, across states, and across life seasons, often with three kids in tow! And I know firsthand that it takes more than logistics to feel truly settled. It takes care, vision, and someone who understands both the details and the emotions behind every decision.<\/p>\n<p>Born in Seoul and raised in London, I\u2019ve lived, studied, and worked in some of the world\u2019s most dynamic cities. With a Master\u2019s in Visual Communication and experience leading boutique hotel renovations in Kensington, I developed a love for well designed spaces and thoughtful living. After getting married in California and raising our young family in Brooklyn, we moved to Georgetown, Texas in 2021, drawn by Austin\u2019s natural beauty, creative spirit, and strong sense of community.<\/p>\n<p>I\u2019m a bilingual speaker of English and Korean, and a real estate professional who brings both lived experience and practical insight to every client relationship. I\u2019ve flipped homes, designed rooms from the studs up, and relocated more times than I can count. That journey helps me to see what really matters when people are making big moves.<\/p>\n<p>Whether you\u2019re starting fresh, looking for more space, or preparing for a new season of life, I\u2019m here to guide you with clarity, creativity, and care. I believe in thoughtful communication, honest guidance, and walking alongside my clients to help them feel seen, heard, and fully supported.<\/p>\n<p>It would be a joy and an honor to help you and your family take the next step toward a place that feels like home.<\/p>\n<p class=\"ms-outlook-mobile-reference-message skipProofing\" dir=\"ltr\">Email: <span style=\"color: #000000;\"><a style=\"color: #000000;\" title=\"mailto:rebekahhjk@gmail.com\" href=\"mailto:rebekahhjk@gmail.com\" data-outlook-id=\"4140c2a0-4e78-4563-ae5e-b9aa86c7540e\">rebekahhjk@gmail.com<\/a><\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"ms-outlook-mobile-reference-message skipProofing\" dir=\"ltr\">Phone number: (213) 440-1415<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4b4b7db elementor-widget elementor-widget-html\" data-id=\"4b4b7db\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"html.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<style>\n.elementor-column.elementor-col-33 ul.elementor-icon-list-items {\n    padding-bottom: 10px;\n}    \n<\/style>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Our Agents Rebekah Kim SALES ASSOCIATE Contact Moving is one of life\u2019s biggest transitions. I\u2019ve done it across countries, across states, and across life seasons, often with three kids in tow! And I know firsthand that it takes more than logistics to feel truly settled. It takes care, vision, and someone who understands both the [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":4,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"elementor_header_footer","meta":{"_vp_format_video_url":"","_vp_image_focal_point":[],"foot